data.description: Welcome to this meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in the heart of Martin County and just minutes from US-1 and downtown Stuart. As you step inside, you'll appreciate the convenience of the digital keypad access that is seamlessly integrated with iPhone control capability and  a Lutron smart dimmer switch. Ample natural light will be abundant with the newly fitted hurricane impact windows illuminating the freshly painted interior and highlighting the seamless flow between the real-wood, tile and laminate flooring. NO CARPET! AC has a new compressor installed in 2023 and you may enjoy effortless climate control at your fingertips with the Nest digital smart thermostat. The galley kitchen has been upgraded with sleek quartz countertops and chic new cabinetry only to be complimented by new stainless steel appliances. A dedicated laundry room is attached to the kitchen adding to the functionality of the home. Enjoy the serenity of the fully screened and covered lanai that is complete with an attached storage room that can be used as a workshop or a safe space for your outdoor essentials. Additional storage is available with the outdoor shed in your fully fenced in backyard. No HOA and LOW TAXES only add to this home's comfort and convenience.
